        <li>Enable token support in testnet</li>
        <li>Enable Liquidity Farming in testnet</li>
        <li>Enable Sandwich-Proof DeFi in testnet</li>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class = "mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Q3 2025</h3>
        <li>Enable P2P Browser Node communication using WebRTC</li>
        <li>Add token support in mainnet</li>
        <li>Add "Copy Balance" feature for newly created tokens in Testnet</li>
